HEADWORD: Elsewhither
<hw>Else"whith`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>To some, or
any, other place; <as>as, you will have to go <ex>elsewhither</ex> for
it</as>.</def> <au>R. of Gloucester.</au> ⟦ldquo⟧For
<xex>elsewhither</xex> was I bound.⟦rdquo⟧
